2.0 2004/05/16 20:55:15
* version updated to 2.00
   -- sorry, no big feature change.  I just hate version 1.100 :)
! lib/Encode/Guess.pm
  Unicode/Unicode.pm
  addressed  UTF-(8|32LE) + BOM misguessing
